{"tid":815450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美民眾怒貼「支那人滾回支那」","createTime":"2018-09-12T05:25:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T15:01:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":219,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"26608e71ce553c643a03e3ee08d8fd3840a7ed59","tid":815450,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:25:24.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國南加州1間豪華住宅驚爆排擠中國人事件，1位當地中國民眾拍攝影片說明因許多中國籍人士不守規矩，將垃圾棄置在住宅內公共空間，被其他住戶製作「支那人滾回支那」的標語洩憤。<br />\n由中國民眾拍攝的影片最早於本月5日上傳於推特，而後被轉傳到影音平台YouTube與其他論壇，1位中國民眾身在美國南加州阿罕布拉市（Alhambra）的「88」高級公寓，他在片中站在公寓走道介紹，「這裡住了大量的中國人，富二代、退休的幹部」。<br />\n<br />\n接著他進入專供住戶傾倒垃圾的公共空間，當中能見牆壁上有道機門，住戶們可打開機門將廢棄物投入，以維持環境整潔，不料中國住戶卻將垃圾囤積在室內空間，導致廚餘類垃圾流出腐敗汁液、臭氣沖天，甚至連超市的購物手推車都被中國民眾藏在此處。<br />\n中國民眾在影片中說道，「他們的所作所為激怒了鄰居，鄰居直接把這個（抗議標語）貼上來了」，從中能見牆上貼著中英對照抗議標語，中文為「支那人滾回支那」，英文為「Locusts back to China」，中國民眾指著「「Locusts」解釋「是蝗蟲的意思，我就不念了，因為沒法念」。<br />\n事件曝光後引發中國民眾不滿，認為此事涉及歧視，也有人懷疑此影片為香港民眾所為，甚至不排除是拍攝影片的男子自導自演，有中國網友指出，「88」高級公寓租金高昂，單人套房每月租金為2500美元（約台幣7萬7084元）起跳，若承租車位則須另付75美元（約台幣2312元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2548202\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2548202&d=3rJsxH%2F%2B72fQ8TF%2FSjX6Mm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=3efcbdbf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2548202&h=2b88e244\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2548202</a>"},{"pid":"66001e0f6a640a1af6ae126844e50b2c1ae3de72","tid":815450,"uid":511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:27:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25986ab224e428ada3b6391e1a8d608ff40c7140","tid":815450,"uid":77959,"like":86,"dislike":2,"score":84,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:29:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">中國民眾指著「「Locusts」解釋「是蝗蟲的意思，我就不念了，因為沒法念」</span><br />\n做乜唔讀自己個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d86ddbfb845886c701097370a567909137bfaa","tid":815450,"uid":41116,"like":51,"dislike":3,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:35:48.000Z","msg":"香港都大把<br />\n一棟樓好地地有管理有人收垃圾<br />\nd 支那人入左去住後可以唔比管理費<br />\n搞搞下就個個唔比 管理都無埋<br />\n之後d 垃圾就掉晒喺自己大夏大門口或者附近舖頭門口<br />\n入夜行下d 支那人聚居地區<br />\n周街都係一袋袋垃圾"},{"pid":"8ee067442c0c928e6e256064f6d045d8e00e685a","tid":815450,"uid":132572,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:36:53.000Z","msg":"邊個連登仔做既認左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又繁體又支又蝗"},{"pid":"ab02e3cb030898c9c0a04fc6d496ca3b213b78b6","tid":815450,"uid":79563,"like":204,"dislike":2,"score":202,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpxhH5zF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpxhH5zF.jpg&h=19930ca5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊個巴打整架?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f8aeaa43b23258c90a6ced14496c724fb759d9","tid":815450,"uid":79563,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"8ee067442c0c928e6e256064f6d045d8e00e685a","tid":815450,"uid":132572,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:36:53.000Z","msg":"邊個連登仔做既認左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又繁體又支又蝗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:39:08.000Z","msg":"當今之世<br />\n<br />\n應該得香港人用「支那」一詞用得最多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a679f3e0a140f88e6c386709fbd1b5f09acd36","tid":815450,"uid":159574,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/up